<paragraph id="91623688FFF8FFD4FF04EACFFC70FE8D" blockId="13.[178,1086,218,299]" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492">
Comment: A female 
<typeStatus id="4E66882AFFF8FFD4FE78EACEFDF5FF56" box="[462,541,219,240]" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492">syntype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="56DD4D0BFFF8FFD4FDF2EACFFCB0FF56" box="[580,856,218,240]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Scymbalium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufotestaceum">
<emphasis id="A3A9EA9AFFF8FFD4FDF2EACFFCB0FF56" box="[580,856,218,240]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492">Scymbalium rufotestaceum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="56DD4D0BFFF8FFD4FF04EAEDFE81FEA8" baseAuthorityName="Reitter" baseAuthorityYear="1887" box="[178,361,248,270]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Micrillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallidus">
<emphasis id="A3A9EA9AFFF8FFD4FF04EAEDFE81FEA8" box="[178,361,248,270]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492">Micrillus pallidus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, from the BMNH had already been examined earlier (
<bibRefCitation id="F54C4B79FFF8FFD4FC13EAEDFBDAFEA8" author="ASSING V" box="[933,1074,248,270]" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492" pagination="301 - 344" refId="ref22718" refString="ASSING V. (2008): A revision of the Micrillus species of the Palaearctic region, with notes on two species from adjacent parts of the Afrotropical and Oriental regions (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde Serie A, Neue Serie 1: 301 - 344." type="journal article" year="2008">ASSING 2008</bibRefCitation>
). The species is reported from 
<collectingCountry id="E9CA7618FFF8FFD4FE6FEB00FDD6FE8D" box="[473,574,277,299]" name="Tajikistan" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492">Tajikistan</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="E9CA7618FFF8FFD4FDD9EB00FD0DFE8D" box="[623,741,277,299]" name="Kazakhstan" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492">Kazakhstan</collectingCountry>
for the first time.
</paragraph>
